description: This file sets up an Express router with a single GET endpoint at /api/reports/velocity, which generates a velocity report by querying 'Issue' model data to count completed issues with status 'done'. It uses middleware for authentication and follows OpenAPI annotations for documentation.

methods.name: GET /api/reports/velocity
methods.description: Handles GET requests to retrieve a velocity report, counting completed issues with status 'done' and returning their count as 'completedIssues'.
